(28525, 'Triple omega 3-6-9 with borage oil 120 softgels', 'تريبل اوميجا 3-6-9 مع زيت لسان الثور 120 كبسولة', '600', '1,050', 'Fish flax & borage oils', 'Puritans pride', 'Gel', 'جل', '', 'Multivitamins', '', 'Under FDA approval, fish oil pharmaceuticals are typically products consisting of a combination of the omega-3-fatty acids eicosapentaenoic acid (EPA) and docosahexaenoic acid (DHA) and are indicated primarily as an adjunct to diet to reduce triglyceride levels in adult patients with severe (>=500 mg/dL) hypertriglyceridemia [FDA Label, F36].
